Text: RE the summary report Cc I am sorry Somehow I confused the ask and bid while thinking whos asking and whos biddingetc I am still not very familiar with this type of market place but I bet I will not be confused bid and ask again Attached is corrected version Original Message From Kaminski Vince J Sent Friday June AM To Kim Jinbaek Cc Lee Bob Subject RE the summary report Jinbaek There is still an error in the definition of the bidoffer spread Can you look into it I have sent it already to Greg Whalley my boss before I caught it Vince Original Message From Kim Jinbaek Sent Friday June AM To Kaminski Vince J Subject FW the summary report How are you doing Attached is the summary of yesterdays presentation you asked me I have no idea whom I should circulate this report So please circulate this report to whom you think appropriate Mark Hall I am going to send this to Zimin and Bob Jinbaek File summarydoc
